v1 <- ggplot(data = meseals, aes(x = year, y = state, fill = incidence + 1/10000, colour = "grey")) + 
  geom_tile()
v1

(4)

ex04 <- v1 + 
  labs(x = "Year",
       y = "States", 
       title = "Meseals Incident Cases by Years",
       caption = "Project Tycho (2019)") + 
  theme(plot.title = element_text(hjust = 0.6))

ex04

ex05 <- ex04 +
  scale_x_continuous(breaks = seq(1930,2000, 10),
                     expand = expansion(0))

ex05

ex06 <- ex05 + 
  scale_y_discrete(limits=rev)

ex06

ex07 <- ex06 +
  scale_fill_distiller(
    palette = "Purples",
    breaks = 10^(-2:3),
    limits = c(2e-3, NA),
    direction = 1,
    labels = prettyNum,
    trans = "log10",
    guide = guide_colourbar(
      frame.colour = "black",
      ticks.colour = "black"
    ),
    name = "Incidents",
    oob = scales::squish,
    na.value = "grey"
  )
ex07

ex08 <- ex07 + 
  scale_colour_manual(values=NA) +
  guides(colour=guide_legend(NA, override.aes=list(colour="black")))
ex08
